<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>My next part here is to ask what people thought of the ending to The Ring? Did anyone get what the Ring really is?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
While what you said about the ring being a cycle could be well, probably is true, I think the more obvious answer to the question is just that the ring was what Samara saw after being trapped in the well.  In the flashback/hallucination/whatever that they showed near the end, when Samara looked up she could see a ring of light coming in around the lid of the well.  If I am remembering correctly, that ring looked exactly like the one in the tape.  According to Rachel, Samara died 7 days after seeing that ring of light, just as viewers died 7 days after seeing the identical ring in the video.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Why did her son freak out when he found out they found the girls body?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
Oooooooh, that was a great moment.  It seemed like everything was all fixed up, and the sudden change in the music tone and the boy's facial expression just sent chills down my spine.  I believe he was so scared because he knew that Samara's intent was always going to be malevolent, regardless of whether or not she was helped, and thus he realized that they hadn't solved the problem at all.  *Shivers*<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Why did Rachelle live while the other guy died?... Why then does Rachelle make another copy of the tape and tells her son to make someone else watch it?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
I think that making the copy was just as vital for one's survival as showing it to others.  Remember that Rachel didn't make the last copy herself; she guided her son's hands as <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>he</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> pressed the buttons to record it.  I believe that in order to truly be spreading Samara's pain, which is what had to be done to not be killed, people would have to both make their own copy of the tape and show it to someone else. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=komikino>komikino</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(10/27/02 1:39:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11319.topic&index=29>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://schleiferstudios.com/dance80.gif height=80 width=80></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: R</span><hr size=1> Interesting points, Wantsomepie. When I saw the &quot;Ring&quot; of light I thought &quot;That's what the ring is!&quot; It was the obvious answer to it but I think the underlying meaning to it is the &quot;evil chain letter&quot; theory I mentioned. <br>
